INSERT INTO `t_product` VALUES (6,19,'双生记银戒指','Twin Story Silver Ring',5000,91,0,'/media/lin/000692EB000B4EA4/j2ee/JeanseLam/src/main/webapp/product_photo/0669ef4f-43a5-4fe1-b214-e07bdddcc47e.png','<div class=\"spec_pic\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" height=\"632\" src=\"http://www.oohdear.com/OhdFileMage/userfiles/images/commodityPhoto/2016/3/20160301154552742.jpg\" width=\"632\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"product_desc \">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.oohdear.com/OhdFileMage/userfiles/images/2016/3/20160301154817.jpg\" style=\"width: 632px; height: 421px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.oohdear.com/OhdFileMage/userfiles/images/2016/3/20160301154824.jpg\" style=\"width: 632px; height: 421px;\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n',1,'双生记',1,'2016-03-01',' 三道光痕，华丽、轻盈地跃动指间的圆舞曲，曼妙地舞动光之印记。锆石星星点点落于肌肤，举手间，魅力绽放。别致的造型、摩登的线条感，呈现现代风尚的迷人气质。简约风格与精致质感，令着装进阶更高品位。\r\n\r\n我的世界中，住着两个自己，藏着秘密的小故事。一个“我”，喜爱清新优雅的气息，那是种曼妙心情，美好如海边微风中的少女；另一个“我”，钟情独立叛逆的风格，像一种奇幻魔力，神秘如夜色星辰里的魅影。如同双生的我，听从自己的内心，无论哪一面都让人入迷。\r\n'),(14,9,'银耳饰','Silver Ear Ring',3000,94,0,'/media/lin/000692EB000B4EA4/j2ee/JeanseLam/src/main/webapp/product_photo/1affce26-559f-4ebe-9731-64cea4f39294.png','<div class=\"spec_pic\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" height=\"632\" src=\"http://www.oohdear.com/OhdFileMage/userfiles/images/commodityPhoto/2016/3/20160301153704120.jpg\" width=\"632\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"product_desc \">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.oohdear.com/OhdFileMage/userfiles/images/2016/3/20160301154042.jpg\" style=\"width: 632px; height: 421px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.oohdear.com/OhdFileMage/userfiles/images/2016/3/20160301154054.jpg\" style=\"width: 632px; height: 421px;\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n',3,'双生记',1,'2016-03-01','繁雪如落英，纷飞飘落，美不可言。以细密的锆石点缀，再现雪灵动之姿。晶莹的锆石恰似雪的纯粹，演绎大片的雪花飞舞的欢喜。棱角分明，丝丝缕缕透出雪片凝结成花的美好。璀璨锆石折射光芒，搭配简约裙装恰到好处。'),(15,6,'银耳饰','Silver Ear Ring',8000,97,0,'/media/lin/000692EB000B4EA4/j2ee/JeanseLam/src/main/webapp/product_photo/88ebdd27-c54c-419e-9d57-b99468c3ebea.pn